1
00:00:00,210 --> 00:00:03,170
This... This is...

2
00:00:06,260 --> 00:00:09,010
Oh, no! I'm so sorry!

3
00:00:09,970 --> 00:00:13,390
I booked the wrong hotel.

4
00:00:13,390 --> 00:00:18,520
I went out of my way to beg the manager
to let you come along,

5
00:00:19,730 --> 00:00:22,560
and now there's only one bed.

6
00:00:25,690 --> 00:00:28,820
I'll go ask if they have another room.

7
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:31,280
I just checked.
They're completely full.

8
00:00:31,610 --> 00:00:33,370
*sigh*

9
00:00:33,620 --> 00:00:34,870
Hinata.

10
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:37,080
Yes?

11
00:00:37,080 --> 00:00:40,250
You really are

12
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:55,640
a total handful.

13
00:00:57,140 --> 00:00:58,140
Huh?
